description: Wyn65 Mobile Food Emporium is taking the deliciously soulful cuisine from Lyn65 Kitchen & Bar that has been winning over the Twin Cities for years, trucking it through town, and delighting every street foodie around. They’re serving up their award-winning fried chicken and famous Southern sides, including Fried Yams, Pimento Mac & Cheese, and more. For a fun & tasty culinary experience you’re sure to adore, come try a taste from Wyn65 Mobile Food Emporium.
name: Wyn65 Mobile Food Emporium
